          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Small Business Emergency Disaster Bridge Loan Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill amends the Small Business Act to authorize the Small Business Administration to provide guaranteed bridge loans (i.e., loans made to small businesses while their applications for assistance under a disaster loan program are pending) to small businesses located in declared major disaster areas.</p>]]></text>
